title: Psycho Watch Face
summary: Psycho watch is crazy B&W watchface for Android Wear
description: Psycho Watch is crazy B&W watch face for Android Wear. The watch face employs very contrast colors and round shapes for all watches. The background is switched from black to white or contrast division background. The hands are thick and rounded. Psycho Watch is the way to express your mood with your watch face. A striking colors made it very easy to spot. The color of hands streaks out of with background so it is easy to read. The big number in background is a day of month. The background can be adapted with settings for different mood and light environment. The relaxed back ground is plain black or white. The psycho background displays very contrast white and black colors. The both moods can be color-inverted.
